attributes.description: Navin Fluorine International Ltd is primary engaged in producing refrigeration gases, inorganic fluorides, specialty organofluorines and offers contract research and manufacturing services.[1] Its portfolio includes 50+ fluorinated compounds developed over the years.[2]
